verbose_text: We performed a CCK-8 assay to explore the effect of hsa_circ_0137606 on cell proliferation; hsa_circ_0137606 knockdown led to significant increases in BC cell proliferation compared with the NC group at 72 and 96 h (XREF_FIG).
evidence: hsa_circ_0137606 knockdown led to significant increases in BC cell proliferation
